en.Text:
A new update has arrived! ECLISE Alpha 4 contains:
- Adventure: Chapter 15 to 18
- Extra Adventure: Night Wild West Pt.2!
- Plant Quest: Strawburst!
- New plant: Chrocus!
- New zombie: Zombie Amber!
- New Warp Party levels & revisits!
- 4 new costumes!
- Tons of QoL and minor changes!
Good luck on your journey, Gardeners. May victory and enjoyment be with you.
